												<div class="description author withsidebar">
													<h6><a href="https://lithub.com/author/emilyjsmith/">Emily J. Smith</a></h6>
													Emily J. Smith is a writer and tech professional based in Brooklyn. She has led teams at top tech companies and founded the dating app, Chorus. She holds a B.S in Electrical and Computer Engineering from Cornell, and an M.B.A. from UC Berkeley’s Haas School of Business. Her writing has appeared in <em>Catapult</em>, <em>The Rumpus</em>, <em>Slate</em>, <em>Vice</em>, <em>WashPo</em>, and others. This is her first novel.																									</div>
